defaultb)default&#xa0;defaultIn the context of question 3, what can we learn from the interaction between the defaultUKdefault courts and the European Court of Justice and European Court of Human Rights?default              
defaultThe conferment of power to hold an Act of Parliament to be unconstitutional might mean that cases that 
